                <![CDATA[Zeekr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[纯电动车]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1234596</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>吉利控股集团旗下电动汽车品牌 Zeekr（极氪）首间香港陈列室 Zeekr Space 今日正式于湾仔开幕投入服务，同场限时展出 1,265 匹马力纯电猎装超跑 Zeekr 001 FR。全能都市型 SUV Zeekr X (港澳右軚版本) 亦将于本月月下旬抵港。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_3-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>陈列室展示 Zeekr 其中两款随即在香港上市的型号 Zeekr 009 及 SUV Zeekr X 之余，更限时展出 1,265 匹马力的纯电猎装超跑 Zeekr 001 FR。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_8-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲纯电猎装超跑 Zeekr 001 FR</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_14-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SUV Zeekr X （左）；纯电猎装超跑 Zeekr 001 FR（右）</p><p>Zeekr Space 陈列室配备开放式的洽谈区和独立的洽谈室，方便销售顾问为顾客提供个人化购买体验。陈列室亦设有品牌精品专区 Zeekr Collection。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_15-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_7-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Zeekr （锦龙汽车）总经理梁栢福表示，为方便客户，Zeekr Space 特地选址湾仔市中心。据梁栢福透露，稍后预计本年 7 月底在太古城开设第二个陈列室，是 Zeekr 在香港的旗舰「品牌体验中心」，旨在打造 Zeekr 高端豪华新能源的品牌形象。 集团计划在 2025 年于香港岛，九龙，新界开设陈列室及售后中心，以及增添充电装置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/zeekr_12-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>地址： 香港湾仔告士打道 39 号夏悫大厦地下 A 舖<br />
服务时间： 星期一至日及公众假期　上午 9 时正至晚上 8 时正</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">新 Tesla Model 3 Performance 抵港　破百 3.1 秒 +  528KM 续航力</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 与百度将达成协议　协助 Tesla FSD 进入中国市场</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/huawei-car-3-dead/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为问界电动车意外焚毁困人酿 3 死　客服查询售后体验 + 问界汽车：电池正常</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/zeekr-space-wan-chai/life-tech/auto/">ZEEKR 全港首间陈列室湾仔开幕　 限时展出纯电超跑 Zeekr 001 FR</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
