            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>cmf by Nothing 这个 Nothing 初创公司的子品牌，除了早前为大家介绍过的抵玩智能手表 Watch Pro 外，同期其实亦推出了一款 $400 有找，同样抵玩的真无线耳机 Buds Pro。定价来说确实是抵玩，但究竟使用起来效果又如何？音质会否有惊喜？就让 Edward 现在为 unwire.hk 们深入评测一下吧。</p><h2>cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 开箱直击</h2><p>一如以往，在为大家分享 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的使用体验前，先让 Edward 为大家来个开箱直击吧。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00579.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的包装盒，今次借测的有两种颜色：浅灰色及橙色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234541" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00581.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234542" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00582.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包装盒上印有产品规格资讯，亦印有它是在中国制造。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234543" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00583.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲与 Watch Pro 一样，Buds Pro 也是采用揭盖式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234544" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00584.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234547" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00587.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲左方揭盖内页印有耳机构造图，以及用作扫描下载 Nothing X APP 作配对耳机的 QR Code。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234545" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00585.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而右方就见到 Buds Pro 耳机充电盒的真身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234546" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00586.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而白色的包装盒内就装有多两对大、细耳塞、USB-C 充电线及说明书。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234548 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1234549 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲基本上由于 Buds Pro 支援 Google 快速配对功能，如果大家使用的是 Android 手机，即使不安装 Nothing X APP 也可以配对耳机的，但就用不到 Nothing X APP 内的调校功能了。至于 iPhone，就一定要安装这个 APP 才可配对得到。</p><h2>佩戴感舒服稳阵不易甩</h2><p>先说外观设计吧：cmf by Nothing 最新推出的 Buds Pro 真无线耳机，采用了圆形的充电盒，有别于一般真无线耳机采用的长方体圆角设计，加上鲜艳吸引的配色（尤其是橙色），确实十分「吸睛」。耳机体积亦不大，十分轻身，笔者以电子磅量度过一对重量也只是 9.9g，戴在双耳十分无感，而且耳塞用料柔软，长时间佩戴耳道亦不觉有不适感。此外，耳机可以十分稳阵佩戴在双耳上，笔者试过即使跑步或跳动也未试过会甩出来，整体使用体验都十分理想，完全不像一款 $400 有找的真无线耳机所带来的体验感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234554" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00588.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 的充电盒，大家可以见到它采用圆形设计，有别于一般真无线耳机采用较长方形充电盒的风格。当中橙色版本肯定是最为抢眼。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234555" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00591.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲充电盒盒底印有 cmf by Nothing 的商标。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234557" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00594-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前方设有指示灯，留意揭开时，有灯的一半部分要在下方，揭开时耳机才会稳稳放在充电盒内。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234558" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00593.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而背后就设有 USB-C 充电插槽，留意 Buds Pro 只能支援有线充电，不支援无线充电的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234559" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00596-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲打开充电盒，就见到 Buds Pro 真身了，而耳机配色与充电盒配色是一样的。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00605.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳柄内侧设有的金属点具备磁吸功能，放在充电盒合适位置就会吸著并开始充电。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234560" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00599.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机设计方面，基本上与一般真无线耳机差不多，不过它的耳柄位就相对较短，令耳机看起来较细只。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234562" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00612.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234563" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00614.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲笔者以电子磅量度，一对耳机的重量也只是 9.9g，十分轻身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00601-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机轻加上体积细，拿在手掌内十分舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234565" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164903.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲即使佩戴在耳朵上，那种轻身程度亦十分无感，而且耳塞物料较为柔软，长时间佩戴耳道也不会觉得辛苦。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234566" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00619.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00616.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而外携使用时，即使耳机连充电盒，重量也只是 54.9g，仍然十分轻身，放在裤袋亦十分轻松。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00603.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳柄位同样印有 cmf by Nothing 的商标，这亦是触控操控耳机的位置。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234570" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00606.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机上这个黑点位置设有感应位，可以感测用家是否已戴上耳机，如是就会自动启动音乐播放等功能。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/cmf-by-nothing-watch-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】cmf by Nothing Watch Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　屏幕　操控体验　使用时间开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/cmf-neckband-pro-cmf-buds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 两款无线耳机   CMF Neckband Pro、CMF Buds With ANC 发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/23/cmf-by-nothing-neckband-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 两款无线耳机，确认 3 月 5 日与 Phone (2a) 一同发表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>音质不过不失低音较逊色</h2><p>至于音质方面，cmf by Nothing 官方未有提及 Buds Pro 采用多大的驱动单元，只是介绍使用了定制的动态低音加强驱动单元，而笔者佩戴后使用，感觉音质算是不错，高清清晰到位，人声亦可清楚听到，不过官方表示的强化低音效果，笔者试听过就只是一般般，不但动态不太足够，而且听起来十分蒙，感觉不算理想。不过如果大家用来听歌时不是欣赏以低音为主的音乐（例如：Jazz、Rock 等），或者用来睇戏听音效时对音质要求不是太高，Buds Pro 的表现也未至于十分差的。不过它的音频解码只支援 AAC 及 SBC，而且亦不支援任何高清音效标准，感觉有点可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00610.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Buds Pro 采用了定制式的动态低音加强驱动单元，笔者试听后听感算不错，人声清晰高音亦到位，不过低音表现就十分一般，即使官方表示加强了低音效果，但听起来仍然比较蒙，不算理想。而且它亦不支援所有高清无线音效标准，有点可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-2.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然，Nothing X APP 内亦设有低音增强的均衡器设定，不过笔者听后觉得改善效果不算明显。</p><h2>降噪表现理想效果舒适</h2><p>至于降噪功能方面，cmf by Nothing Buds Pro 拥有 5000Hz 降噪频率范围，而且支援降低最多 45dB 噪音，同时在可以过滤噪音、风声之余，亦支援清晰话音技术。至于表现方面，笔者就试过佩戴著 Buds Pro 乘搭地铁，并同时用它欣赏音乐，表现算是不错，降噪效果不会太焗促，以免令用家感觉处身在密闭空间的同时，亦可以有效滤走外间噪音。另外，笔者用 Buds Pro 与朋友通话，效果亦十分不错，即使在地铁车箱内，对方仍可清晰听到笔者话声，效果令人满意。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-3.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Buds Pro 支援主动式降噪功能，在这价位的真无线耳机来说算是不太常见，而笔者试用过感觉不错，有不俗的隔音效果，但同时又不会太焗促，以这价位的真无线耳机而言算是有惊喜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/dsc00608.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，耳机上的收音咪亦支援清晰话音技术，笔者试过在地铁车箱内与别人通话，对方也可清晰听到笔者所说的内容。</p><h2>功能不多偏向基本</h2><p>最后功能方面，说是 Buds Pro，它基本上就真的只是一款真无线耳机，就是用来听歌、睇戏时听音效或者通话的耳机，其他功能不多。另外，操控方面，依然是采用在耳机机身透过触控方法控制的方式，使用上亦十分方便，灵敏度亦高。此外，它亦支援 IP54（只限耳机）生活防水防尘功能，亦支援 Google 及 Microsoft 的快速配对模式，整体算是十分基本：未有惊喜但不算令人失望。至于使用时间方面，单是耳机最长可提供 11 小时音乐播放时间，而配合充电盒可提供最长 39 小时音乐播放，以入门级真无线耳机来说表现算是合格以上。即使没电，使用充电盒为耳机充电 10 分钟，已可为耳机带来 5 小时音乐播放时间，算是不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164926.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲透过触控模式就可以用手指在耳机耳柄位操控各功能，十分直觉化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234577" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-4.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如果用家有安装 Nothing X APP，亦可以在 APP 内调校耳机触控不同次数对应操控哪种功能，可将操控个人化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/screenshot_20240228_-5.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，虽然 Buds Pro $400 有找，但它依然支援低延迟模式，同样有惊喜。</p><h2>总结：定价抵玩表现符合预期</h2><p>总括来说，今次 cmf by Nothing 推出的 Buds Pro 真无线耳机，整体表现算是中规中矩：设计固然出色吸睛，降噪效果亦十分理想，但其他功能只属基本，音质上虽然高音及人声表现不俗，但官方标榜的低音表现却是很一般，亦未支援任何无线音效标准。当然，作为一款 $400 有找，而且具有一定设计风格的真无线耳机，在如此抵玩的定价下，其实 Buds Pro 的表现也是符合预期，甚至已是比预期要理想，所以这些缺点，也不算是太大问题了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1234539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240229_164802.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/08/cmf-by-nothing-watch-pro-review/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】cmf by Nothing Watch Pro　外形　佩戴感　功能　屏幕　操控体验　使用时间开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/cmf-neckband-pro-cmf-buds-launched/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 两款无线耳机   CMF Neckband Pro、CMF Buds With ANC 发表</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/23/cmf-by-nothing-neckband-pro/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">CMF by Nothing 两款无线耳机，确认 3 月 5 日与 Phone (2a) 一同发表</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/cmf-by-nothing-buds-pro-review/review-2/">【评测】cmf by Nothing Buds Pro　外形　佩戴感　音质　降噪　功能开箱评测</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
